Title: Flying Colors
Description:
You have passed every test we prepared for you, $n. It is now time for you to move on to bigger and better things.

...but not before another banquet. The High Elder will be waiting for you at the banquet grounds to celebrate your graduation from our monastery.
ObjectivesText: Report to High Elder Cloudfall at the Tian Monastery in the Jade Forest.
RewardText:
Congratulations, $n. While your traineeship was strictly honorary, your results were undeniably impressive. The young ones look up to you.

Groundskeeper Wu had this prepared for you. Please, use it as you see fit.
